---
source: crates/component-frontend/src/components/ds/tabs.rs
expression: "crate::components::ds::pretty_html(&render(\"tabs\", \"06\", \"Tabs & Pills\",\n\"Segmented controls for binary scoping; underline tabs for sub-views; pills for filterable chips.\",))"
---
<section class="pt-12 md:pt-16" id="tabs">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[600px_1fr] gap-6 md:gap-12">
    <div>
      <div class="text-[12px] mono uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-500">
        06
      </div>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-[24px] font-semibold tracking-tight">
        Tabs & Pills
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-[13px] text-ink-500 leading-relaxed">
        Segmented controls for binary scoping; underline tabs for sub-views; pills for filterable chips.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[13px] mono uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-500 mb-3">
          Segmented
        </h3>
        <div class="flex p-1 rounded-lg bg-surfaceMuted w-[200px]">
          <button class="flex-1 h-7 rounded-md bg-ink-900 text-canvas text-[13px] font-medium">
            Lorem
          </button>
          <button class="flex-1 h-7 rounded-md text-[13px] text-ink-500">
            Ipsum
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[13px] mono uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-500 mb-3">
          Underline tabs
        </h3>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 border-b-[1.5px] border-rule">
          <button class="relative pb-3 text-[15px] font-medium">
            Aenean
            <span class="absolute left-0 right-0 -bottom-[1.5px] h-[1.5px] bg-ink-900">
            </span>
          </button>
          <button class="pb-3 text-[15px] text-ink-500">
            Mauris
          </button>
          <button class="pb-3 text-[15px] text-ink-500">
            Vivamus
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[13px] mono uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-500 mb-3">
          Panel tabs
        </h3>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="id-lang-tabs">
            <span class="id-lang-tab is-active" style="background: var(--c-canvas);">
              <span class="dot">
              </span>
              CLI
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-lineSoft rounded-md rounded-tl-none bg-canvas p-4">
            <div class="flex">
              <span aria-hidden class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 h-7 rounded-l-md border border-r-0 border-line bg-surfaceMuted text-[12.5px] text-ink-500 mono select-none">
                $
              </span>
              <code class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 h-7 rounded-r-md border border-line bg-surface mono text-[12.5px] text-ink-900 whitespace-nowrap">
                component install wasi:http@0.2.4
              </code>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[12px] text-ink-500">
          Tabbed surface for grouping a primary action with related content. Active tab fuses with the padded panel below; the panel can host a copy box, prose, or additional controls. Used for the install section on package pages.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
